						<summary>

						<p>This is incised in modern characters, and is damaged, It is dated in Jaya, Vaigāśi 17, and seems to regīster a gift of land to a certain Śivala Peddinā[ya*]kkaṉ, son of Bommināyakkaṉ who was a servant of Tirumalai Chinna Pāppanāyakkar.</p>						

